    <title>在blog上传视频</title>
    <link href="/2025/02/07/%E5%9C%A8blog%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/"/>
    <url>/2025/02/07/%E5%9C%A8blog%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><span id="more"></span><p>如何将B站视频放到自己的网站上(将B站作为图片图床使用)</p><p>首先在B站复制视频的嵌入代码</p><p><strong>如下图</strong></p><p><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67a5d67fd0e0a243d4fc8fcb.png"></p><p>然后在自己的.md文件中粘贴代码(这样直接复制话,视频的清晰度低,画面小,还会自动播放)</p><p>接下来的步骤是来解决上述问题的</p><p><strong>原代码如下:</strong></p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">&lt;iframe <span class="hljs-attribute">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&amp;aid=113956102343677&amp;bvid=BV1cJNJe8Env&amp;cid=28242805217&amp;p=1&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">scrolling</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">border</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">frameborder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">framespacing</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">allowfullscreen</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>改进后的代码:</strong></p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">&lt;iframe <span class="hljs-attribute">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&amp;aid=113956102343677&amp;bvid=BV1cJNJe8Env&amp;cid=28242805217&amp;p=1&amp;autoplay=0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;100%&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;500&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">scrolling</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">border</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">frameborder</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;no&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">framespacing</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">allowfullscreen</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1.在src最后添加&amp;autoplay&#x3D;0可以使视频不会自动播放</p><p>2.在src外添加width&#x3D;”100%” height&#x3D;”500”可以调整网页上视频的大小</p><p>下方为嵌入视频实例(樊振东巴黎决赛)</p><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=113138884215496&bvid=BV1dS4CekEyH&cid=25863916065&p=1&autoplay=0" width="100%" height="500" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>]]></content>
    
    
